{"tid":417891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] King’s Raid #16 請勿使用外掛/MOD/修改版進行遊戲","createTime":"2017-09-29T06:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T08:03:33.000Z","uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0e8f9f85fd9bfce717e039a75c93494415581c","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Sever【Asia】</span></strong></span><br />\n需入公會嘅巴絲請留言提供ID，謝謝合作<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/204618_be489187f7143ee02f5231916e99e451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F204618_be489187f7143ee02f5231916e99e451.jpg&h=204a42c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKing`s Raid(簡稱KR)<br />\n橫向類型遊戲<br />\n戰鬥畫面打擊感強，角色精美<br />\n技能、職業種類多各有用途<br />\n玩家可以組合屬於自己既隊伍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174135_9c2624011a20e6ecbc02e0c14535660d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174135_9c2624011a20e6ecbc02e0c14535660d.jpg&h=7fb1cbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ANDROID</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F4943&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=adde9df2\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IOS</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fkings-raid%2Fid1097735195&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c4ecdb2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195</a><br />\n已經收到由 香港 巴打提供嘅美國AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如有需要借用可以聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King's Raid 新手入門【By湯丸】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 各職專武繁中翻譯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 全人物覺醒表 v1.2【繁中版】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 英雄評價表【連登版】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 2,3,5星券揀咩角色好呀?(5星為活動券,通常係活動期間登入夠7日就有,每日重置時間為香港時間零晨1點)<br />\nA:隊形一般會選擇1坦2輸出1奶<br />\n2星券,<span style=\"color: red;\">紅框為首選</span>(Gau係戰士,可做坦可做物理輸出,Kaulah為牧師,用途較廣)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174055_47837c961a4a610cdb7ecfcaf1525ed2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174055_47837c961a4a610cdb7ecfcaf1525ed2.jpg&h=d1d0a8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3星券,<span style=\"color: red;\">紅框為冇活動5星券既首選DPS</span>,<span style=\"color: purple;\">紫框為有活動5星券首選多控場副DPS</span>,<span style=\"color: green;\">綠框為有活動5星券可選角色</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174021_7ac5652dda98c56113ef53421a28a573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174021_7ac5652dda98c56113ef53421a28a573.jpg&h=9c6f8b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5星券,<span style=\"color: red;\">紅框為首選DPS</span>,<span style=\"color: green;\">綠框為次選DPS</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/182455_ca39beb218941c55b59be1f9b18bd2c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F182455_ca39beb218941c55b59be1f9b18bd2c4.jpg&h=58227264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講就講曬,仲有選擇困難既就問你自己細佬啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ:咁其他角色呢?唔揀係咪即係廢?<br />\nA:唔係,大部分角色都有各自既用途同玩法,有D係打龍勁,有D係PVP勁,有D係打BOSS勁,有D係推圖勁,仲有分前期角同後期角,不過玩耐左就會明,只係開頭揀勁既DPS黎用姐<br />\n<br />\nQ:我個隊應該點配呀?<br />\nA:一隊入面一般配置就係1坦2輸出1奶,其中一個輸出會係拎黎控場(控場技能即係CC)用既副DPS,因為控場可以打斷敵人既技能,例如係敵人吟唱時間你暈佢,佢就冇得出依招技,係PVP黎講甚至會令對手冇埋Mana(Mana=出技cost),進而令你較容易獲勝<br />\n<br />\nQ：需唔需要刷首抽架？<br />\nA：冇首抽依回事，角色可以用自選卷,用石買同係酒館到溝返黎，專武就每日免費抽都有機會中<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩英好用？<br />\nＡ：評價表：<br />\n鬼佬版：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/KRzAey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FKRzAey&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9e6d818e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/KRzAey</a><br />\n連登版：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/qvtP8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FqvtP8A&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8b8c033a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/qvtP8A</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：D武器裝備點搞啊？點分？<br />\nA：專武T10(得武器有專武 - 一開始會送男劍專武一把)<br />\n金(RAID/商店金抽/紅石抽)<br />\n紅(主線HARD/HELL MODE/RAID/商店金抽/紅石抽)<br />\n紫(主線HARD/HELL MODE/RAID/商店金抽/紅石抽)<br />\n藍(分解)<br />\n綠白(分解)<br />\n<br />\nQ：卡主線點搞？<br />\nA：試下睇一次自動打，咩原因卡先<br />\n如果喺唔夠力嘅就升下角升下裝<br />\n如果喺死喺Boss出技嘅話可以等隻王出技嘅時候出CC技斷佢<br />\n<br />\nQ：幾LV封頂？<br />\nＡ：80，英雄1至80級所需經驗 <a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZTSaJj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZTSaJj&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e8c0ec4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZTSaJj</a><br />\n<br />\n如有更多問題可詳見【LIHKG】King's Raid 新手入門【By湯丸】或回覆<br />\n即有專人回答您<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0e91a6e9a16d9b4f9f3d92c5d051ed849780367a","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>囡囡J圖吸客區</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/213342_b99b2f2f055437a55e0cab7f23f514fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F213342_b99b2f2f055437a55e0cab7f23f514fe.jpg&h=6ef6883a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/213350_7c75c9dead258cad8cd6ef2dbc39a6db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F213350_7c75c9dead258cad8cd6ef2dbc39a6db.jpg&h=c7d06d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/213359_e7345700406bf1cf4d2a44ccbbba8c33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F213359_e7345700406bf1cf4d2a44ccbbba8c33.jpg&h=fcd5e9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">仔仔J圖吸客區</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174805_a47fa265a39d13989cf2c72d8c59d14a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174805_a47fa265a39d13989cf2c72d8c59d14a.jpg&h=445c8f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174743_88a69e365737debbff11c57785383c06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174743_88a69e365737debbff11c57785383c06.jpg&h=942e67b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174748_00bcba74c7dfba53fb3e2ed36faa9b2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174748_00bcba74c7dfba53fb3e2ed36faa9b2f.jpg&h=6015105b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>人外J圖吸客區</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174839_c72e4e9de297804e211fafa10f015290.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174839_c72e4e9de297804e211fafa10f015290.jpg&h=4cb37a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174844_0815e732bb868667293a5797b98a252b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174844_0815e732bb868667293a5797b98a252b.jpg&h=1a9c9bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174848_c5f87788921150b2bcd3917068aa8147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174848_c5f87788921150b2bcd3917068aa8147.jpg&h=6a4a1aab&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9a7f75aa71a10d1e7ce79c74ea3e7968afb76e6d","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[iOS Update Delay Reward Announcement] <br />\n▶ Currently, we are setting up rewards for raiders those who could not connect to the game <br />\nafter the maintenance on 28th Sep 2017 due to iOS issue. We will be back with more <br />\ndetails soon about this. <br />\n<br />\n[Event Error Reward Announcement] <br />\n<br />\n▶ There is a bug where some users could not participate in &lsquo;Light Up King&rsquo;s Raid&rsquo; and <br />\n&lsquo;Open the Treasure Chest&rsquo; event after the maintenance on 28th Sep 2017 <br />\nWe will extract the list of all users who could not attend the event after the maintenance. <br />\n<br />\n- Once it&rsquo;s done, we will distribute reward items as much as the amount <br />\nyou did not receive. We will be back with more details soon. <br />\n<br />\n:: Also 100 rubies will be given, which is the final reward for Light Up King&rsquo;s Raid<br />\n<br />\n[Luna&rsquo;s 7 Day Attendance Check Extension] <br />\n▶ Luna&rsquo;s 7 Day Attendance ended after maintenance on 28th Sep 2017. We apologize for <br />\nthe inconvenience that some users did not receive 7th-day reward. <br />\nSo, we are going to activate the event again through today&rsquo;s Urgent Maintenance, and you will<br />\nbe able to receive attendance rewards. <br />\n<br />\n[Stamina Pay Back &amp; Tower of Ordeals Rewards] <br />\n▶ We are going to deliver rewards for &lsquo;Stamina Pay Back&rsquo; and &lsquo;Tower or Ordeals&rsquo; Event <br />\n(Period: 22nd Sep &ndash; 28th Sep) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\niOS入唔到會有補償 遲D再公布<br />\n<br />\nEVENT有補償 100鑽 同埋佢地會搵番尋日冇玩活動嘅人出黎 (輸巴: 多舊魚!)<br />\n<br />\n7日簽到重開 冇講會唔會延長<br />\n<br />\n會派番對上兩個完全冇反應嘅活動嘅獎勵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重開意思 唔會係重新7日再黎過掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知 係嘅話我地發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重開，重新再等7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/140659_166ef7891dbb8db3f4ec1b736ed52c73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F140659_166ef7891dbb8db3f4ec1b736ed52c73.jpg&h=2e22012a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"491852abdcfd2c504a0ecdac8858fc2fca6ea138","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家冷靜d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多人嘈 官方一定會做野既<br />\n<br />\nBtw 刷hell除左打手T2 坦係唔係都要起碼T1 其他5星都得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇咁簡單 我p姐有專t2打唔過...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nT1 laias T3 luna T2 maria T2膠<br />\n都過唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （我知我裝備廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">t5 nyx 表示auto 30秒一場hell 1-8</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1564d786e6c2e7835b8b1d184e27f694abf771c6","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家d鑽通常愛黎抽武器定買角色？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nre</blockquote><br />\nskin"},{"pid":"a3178e791edfa213a4dcc9217c49d0b876b49b89","tid":417891,"uid":19181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5fb0349633e00cbf92763e648c7c8c211dbc8773","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://images.plurk.com/1U857bB3x2M8UmhWv8QE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.plurk.com%2F1U857bB3x2M8UmhWv8QE.jpg&h=b72c963c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撞到BUG, 見佢個daily ruby pack又有得賣, 就狗衝去買<br />\n結果錢就俾左, 但個PACK又買唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫緊信去REFUND <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申: 睇返我上個月買既daily ruby pack, 原來仲有2日, 所以先買唔到<br />\n唔知點解daily ruby pack會著返燈俾我重買</blockquote><br />\n維護完好鬼多BUG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f23dd0ce285ff49b0fbbf25a1c54cdbdd8583ec","tid":417891,"uid":104195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"個post名好仆街呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nm巴 我信你冇用外掛 <br />\n快啲寫埋封信佢啦 <br />\n3會等你番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd64d013b76f488cc684536b546a4134b957abdc","tid":417891,"uid":19181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:36:21.000Z","msg":"維到四點"},{"pid":"e63a6d45cc385b27e0f1318831b7ab545a1f0d4b","tid":417891,"uid":19181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個post名好仆街呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nm巴 我信你冇用外掛 <br />\n快啲寫埋封信佢啦 <br />\n3會等你番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322b26faec8cc100e50688566497b9ea3ee5f465","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"新POST，依個開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/417906/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/417906/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5172f3653b5aa8a6da991c2126aaad9e6867a857","tid":417891,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.plug.game/kingsraid-en#/posts/4036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plug.game%2Fkingsraid-en%23%2Fposts%2F4036&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3a640a47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.plug.game/kingsraid-en#/posts/4036</a><br />\n<br />\n[Event] Autumn Celebration Event<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/160208_d36854d53353dcddb971adf937700dc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F160208_d36854d53353dcddb971adf937700dc7.jpg&h=1808f197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGreetings, Raiders!<br />\nThis time, we brought you another great Autumn Event!<br />\n<br />\nWow! There are too many reward items!<br />\nPlease check the details below!<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n[Autumn Celebration Event!] <br />\n<br />\nPeriod: 2nd Oct after maintenance &ndash; 24:00, 15th Oct 2017 <br />\n** Please note that the event period may change if maintenance schedule changes. <br />\n<br />\nDetails: Collect Rice Cakes and exchange them to various presents! <br />\n<br />\n- You will get 1 &ndash; 5 Rice Cakes with a random rate by clearing stages. <br />\n(Stages by using Stamina) <br />\n- You will also get Rice Cakes by using rubies: 10 Rubies to 1 Rice Cake <br />\n(You can acquire max 1500 Rice Cakes with Rubies) <br />\n- You can acquire 1 &ndash; 5 Rice cakes by clearing Dragon Raids. <br />\n<br />\n** A Loot Booster can be applied for acquiring more amounts of rice cakes in dungeons <br />\nand dragon raids. <br />\n<br />\n** You cannot acquire rice cakes by using rubies as listed; <br />\n<br />\n- Removing Runes <br />\n- Reforge Equipment <br />\n- List Reset<br />\n- Upper Dungeon Reset (All Chapters / Difficulty) <br />\n- Conquest Reset (All Chapters / Difficulty) <br />\n- Stockade Reset <br />\n- Arena Reset <br />\n- Crafting <br />\n- Inventory Expansion<br />\n<br />\n** You can check your current rice cakes through &ldquo;EVENT&rdquo; window.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/160306_cd3fb3ebda89a346fe8ee6b928c3fc24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F160306_cd3fb3ebda89a346fe8ee6b928c3fc24.jpg&h=ac300697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Rice Cake Exchange List] <br />\n<br />\n:: 25 Rice Cakes &ndash; Autumn Gift Box (Unlimited Exchange) <br />\n:: 100 Rice Cakes &ndash; Intermediate Enchant Box (Can be exchanged max 10 times) <br />\n:: 300 Rice Cakes &ndash; Stone of Infinity x1 (Can be exchanged max 3 times) <br />\n:: 900 Rice Cakes &ndash; Artifact Piece x1000 (Can be exchanged once) <br />\n:: 900 Rice Cakes &ndash; Random Unique Weapon Ticket x1 (Can be exchanged once) <br />\n<br />\n- Autumn Gift Box List &ndash; <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/160306_c933d4833399bd8eb76dedb821d573e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F160306_c933d4833399bd8eb76dedb821d573e7.png&h=eb0b93c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n** Listed items can be acquired with a different rate. <br />\n** You can acquire Unique Weapon x1 with a low rate. <br />\n<br />\n- Intermediate Enchant Box - <br />\n<br />\n- You can acquire Rare &ndash; Ancient Enchant Scrolls for 4 Dragons <br />\n<br />\n** Unused rice cakes will vanish after the event period. <br />\n** Rewards will be sent directly to your mailbox. <br />\n<br />\nI hope you enjoy this amazing event!<br />\n<br />\nThank you!<br />\nGM Orvel</div>"}]}